{"atom_id": "md_dmCO_ex_a004", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/CO/examples.md", "line_start": 7, "line_end": 7, "verbatim": "**Row 2:** Shows a comment that was collected on the bottom of the PE page for Visit 7, without any indication of specific records it applied to. Since the comment related to a specific domain, RDOMAIN is populated. Since it was related to a specific visit, VISIT, COREF is \"VISIT 7\". However, since it does not relate to a specific record, IDVAR and IDVARVAL are null.", "parent_section": "§CO.1 [Example 1]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-05T23:30:00Z"}}
