{"atom_id": "md_dmCO_ex_a008", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/CO/examples.md", "line_start": 15, "line_end": 15, "verbatim": "**Row 6:** Shows one option for representing a comment collected on a visit-specific comments page not associated with a particular domain. In this case, the comment is linked to the Subject Visit record in SV (RDOMAIN = \"SV\") and IDVAR and IDVARVAL are populated link the comment to the particular visit.", "parent_section": "§CO.1 [Example 1]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-05T23:30:00Z"}}
